    "description": "Develop the ultimate vaccine in Metavaxx, the world's first minesweeper shooter!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour mission is to train your new vaccine in a selection of various body samples. In each one, you'll have to identify infected cells using your minesweeper detective skills, and either shoot down those cells and the agents hidden inside them, or clear the way around them, only removing the healthy cells. You win when there are either only healthy cells remaining, or only infected cells remaining. The more cells remain, the more points you'll get to level-up your vaccine with unique upgrades!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCarefully choose the order of your body samples, select your upgrades wisely, and try to make the most efficient and accessible vaccine to save as many people as you can around the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAsk your doctor if Metavaxx is right for you!",
